description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Daily Guided Pranayama for Inner Balance | 10 mins | Beginner Level' from the channel Satvic Yoga.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Today's practice will not only help you energise your body and mind but also balance your Agya Chakra which is responsible for clarity of thought, intuition and a sharp intellect.
